quran[16]{c,v,t}:
  15,45,Hubaal kuwa iska jira (xumaha) waxay dhex ahaan doonaan Beero iyo ilo
  15,46,Ku gala nabad idinkoo aamin ah
  15,47,"Oo Waxaan ka soo siibi doonnaa wixii xasad ah oo ku jira laabahooda, (waxay ahaan) walaalo ku sugan sariiro boqoreed dushood is qaabilsan fool ka fool"
  15,48,"Kuma taaban doono gudaheeda daal, lagamana soo saari doono"
  15,49,"Ogeysii addoomahayga inaan Anigu ahay Dambi Dhaaf Badanaha, Naxariista Badan"
  15,50,"Iyo in Cadaabkaygu, kaasi weeye cadaabka xanuunka badan"
  15,51,Oo u sheeg arrinka martidii Ibraahiim
  15,52,"Markay u soo galeen, waxay yidhaadeen: Nabad ahaada. Wuxuu yidhi: hubaal innagu cabsi ayaa idinka qabnaa"
  15,53,"Waxay yidhaahdeen: Ha cabsan. Hubaal waxaan kuugu bishaareyneynaa wiil aqoon leh (dhalashada Isxaaq)"
  15,54,"Wuxuu yidhi: Ma waxaad iigu bishaareyneysaan (wiil) anigoo ay i soo taabatay da' weyni? Haddaba maxaad iigu bishaarayneysaan"
  15,55,"Waxay yidhaahdeen: Waxaan kuugu bishaaraynaynaa wax run ah. Ee ha ka mid noqon kuwa quusta"
  15,56,"Wuxuu yidhi: Oo yaa ka quusta Naxariista Rabbigii aan ahayn kuwa lunsan"
  15,57,"Wuxuu yidhi: Waa maxay howsha aad u socotaan haddaba, kuwaan la soo dirayow"
  15,58,"Waxay yidhaahdeen: Hubaal waxaa naloo soo diray qolo dambiilayaal ah"
  15,59,Reer Luud ma’ahee. Hubaal waanu badbaadin doonnaa xaqiiq iyagoo dhan
  15,60,"Marwadiisa ma’ahee, waxaan qaddarnay inay hubaal ka mid ahaato kuwa ku haraya gadaal (ee la cadaabi)"